{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9fee4bab14","title":"江青、陈伯达、康生接见专王任重革命造反团时的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"40000c8047","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":4,"articleId":"9fee4bab14"}],"tags":[{"id":"57eea82497","name":"康生","type":"人物"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"8b05ac46d8","name":"王任重","type":"人物"},{"id":"dbcf15bd08","name":"陶铸","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","name":"中共党史教学参考资料 第25册 “文化大革命”参考资料 上册（1988年）","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"},{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"8bb7755376","name":"康生"}]},"publication_details":{"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1240bffcb2","type":"paragraph","text":"（已停印人民日报、解放军报、光明日报的代印厂，接到这个通知后，请把它印出来张帖在工厂内）","index":0,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"e61d04ac4c","type":"paragraph","text":"江青、陈伯达、康生接见专拟王任重","index":1,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"949dd9a3dc","type":"paragraph","text":"革命造反团时的讲话","index":2,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"403d671b09","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年一月四日）","index":3,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"3c878e200f","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达讲话","index":4,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"7e257e2773","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸同志到中央来并没有执行以毛主席为代表的无产阶级革命路线，实际是刘、邓路线的忠实执行者。刘、邓路线的推广是同他有关系的，他洗刷这一点，但后来变本加历。例如你们到中南局去，你们了解很多情况，是有后台老板的，一个后台老板就是陶铸。他在北京接见你们的态度是完全错误的，他是文化革命小组顾问，但对文化革命的许多问题，从来没有跟我们商量过。他独断专行，不但背着文革小组，而且背着党中央，你们揭得很好，给我们很多支持，感谢你们","index":5,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"0109b4a756","type":"paragraph","text":"江青讲话同学们：","index":6,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"b081fc9590","type":"paragraph","text":"你们回去斗争要注意两条：一条是实事求是，核实材料，才能立于不败之地；二要做限苦细致的工作，争取多数，不要把敌人看成铁板一块，多数派同学，很多是受蒙骗了，不是不能做工作的，是可以分割的，一定要做细致的工作，这是策略问题，希望大家注意这几点。","index":7,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"25c5f6f8aa","type":"paragraph","text":"康生讲话同志们：","index":8,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"ca69b17a28","type":"paragraph","text":"把材料整理出来，有材料摆出来了，你们就胜利了。再见！","index":9,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"0a6cff67e6","type":"paragraph","text":"【附）","index":10,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"f191b813f8","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸同志被打下台的真相","index":11,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"22f6cd7e54","type":"paragraph","text":"家琼","index":12,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"86fb5c4df2","type":"paragraph","text":"望不尽浩气贯虹象生辉，怀不尽职耿丹心射座；恨不尽妖廉切齿诱忠骨，烧不尽革命烈火旋污秒。每当我读到这几句诗的时候，总是禁不住心潮酒涌，深深怀念起我们所尊敬的陶铸同志。","index":13,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"f270517efe","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年一月四日以前的短短几个月里，因为工作关系，我曾和陶铸同志有过一些难","index":14,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"},{"id":"a927a9447a","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":15,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14"}],"page":{"id":"aa5d15572b","publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"9fee4bab14","start":237,"end":237}}}},"__N_SSG":true}